{"tid":10850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港寬頻被改名「香港寬帶」","createTime":"2016-11-29T05:51:12.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T06:27:48.000Z","uid":36544,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"60c81d79cda7a3a0e49877560d899c1a61e13216","tid":10850,"uid":36544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:51:12.000Z","msg":"香港寬頻被改名「香港寬帶」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20161129&amp;guid=55979885&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20161129%26guid%3D55979885%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant&d=Sk6y7wLkZ8LsH37jlkaP90sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=f285a4be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20161129%26guid%3D55979885%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant&h=4e8126c6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20161129&amp;guid=55979885&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n<br />\n中港矛盾，文化差異，喺「深港通」之下進一步淡化！點解咁講，話說上星期深交所公佈深股通股票暫定名單，作為一個炒友，係咁而都要碌下張List。但睇到中間，你會發現有一間公司，喺中港融合之下被改名！股票編號1310，即係「香港寬頻」，喺深交所「深港通」名單下，你會見到佢個名，竟然係&hellip;竟然係&hellip;「香港寬帶」！<br />\n<br />\n媽呀！如果係咁，咁點解「數碼通」（315）唔使改做「數字通」？就算內地人唔知咩係「寬頻」，夾硬轉個名叫「香港寬帶」&hellip;對內地投資者來講，上網Search「香港寬帶」就得個吉，投資前點做功課？神奇！頂級！超卓。"},{"pid":"dd30ede5164c1b5672fa27ef90542cb47dc67011","tid":10850,"uid":13082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T06:03:18.000Z","msg":"屌，好侮辱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12a120dfa65b99a27be5bb3afe7b130d32550f57","tid":10850,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T06:04:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁鳩嘅名"},{"pid":"e875e1a9e210f8d2a1cbf28cc2fbc0d4c5c86d07","tid":10850,"uid":32650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T06:06:24.000Z","msg":"尼個真係柒"},{"pid":"6d5dfdbeaab63894426e7c5e9e4f0f4acc858487","tid":10850,"uid":25556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T06:10:34.000Z","msg":"broadband直譯？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢老味google translate都係譯broadband做寬帶..."},{"pid":"b56262b604a8911692c3a7df54dee13e8dc487a4","tid":10850,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T06:16:16.000Z","msg":"直接改中國做狗啦咁"},{"pid":"38c96844caef15eb520fac5cd5e29cdda8b86dfc","tid":10850,"uid":14269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T06:24:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/29/142438_3a0d973c7d13f112724759af3b1c8229.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F29%2F142438_3a0d973c7d13f112724759af3b1c8229.jpg&h=a4354e0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n快d改埋個廣告佢啦屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b6a101c95c7e262d28cddab0d05d541bb5c64f2","tid":10850,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T06:27:48.000Z","msg":"弱撚智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 名都有得改"}]}